From: Theseus <https://github.com/ming2k/wright>
Subject: [PATCH] default xwayland-satellite off for pure-Wayland systems

Theseus is a pure native Wayland desktop and does not ship XWayland or
xwayland-satellite. Flip the default for XwaylandSatellite.off to true so
that niri does not try to spawn xwayland-satellite at startup on systems
without a user-supplied config. Users who want X11 compatibility can
re-enable it in their config with `xwayland-satellite { on; }`.

--- a/niri-config/src/misc.rs
+++ b/niri-config/src/misc.rs
@@ -172,7 +172,7 @@ pub struct XwaylandSatellite {
 impl Default for XwaylandSatellite {
     fn default() -> Self {
         Self {
-            off: false,
+            off: true,
             path: String::from("xwayland-satellite"),
         }
     }
